<refsect1>
<title>Examples</title>
<programlisting>
&lt;Limit LOGIN&gt;
Order allow,deny
Allow from 128.44.26.,128.44.26.,myhost.mydomain.edu,.trusted-domain.org
Deny from all
&lt;/Limit&gt;
</programlisting>
